            <property name="toolTip">
             <string>Format tokens:
d / dd    – day (1 or 01)
M / MM    – month (1 or 01)
yyyy      – 4-digit year
yy        – 2-digit year
h / hh    – hour 0-23 (1 or 01)
m / mm    – minute (1 or 01)
s / ss    – second (1 or 01)
dddd      – full day name
MMMM      – full month name

Examples:
dd.MM.yyyy HH:mm:ss  →  05.06.2025 14:30:00
yyyy-MM-dd           →  2025-06-05
dddd d. MMMM yyyy    →  Thursday 5. June 2025</string>
            </property>
